{"tid":1470312,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我地要講清楚，手足尋曰想捉嘅係延伸嘅警權，唔係普通市民記者！！","createTime":"2019-08-14T04:52:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T09:54:11.000Z","uid":182291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"ac3dcb2f8997d033576b1d34c0f23a23990e30b3","tid":1470312,"uid":182291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:52:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我地唔係白衣人，唔係福建幫，唔係黑社會</span><br />\n<br />\n我地唔係見人就打，見著記者衫記者證嘅記者都打，大肚婆都打無差別嘅暴力。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n尋日我地想阻止嘅係濫權濫捕嘅臥底警員/公安，係暴虐政權、警權嘅延伸。</span>而唔係路過嘅旅客、市民、采訪緊嘅記者。<br />\n<br />\n我地要反問政府，我地過去機場集合都好和平，係邊個令到示威者依家和平示威都要擔驚受怕，疑神疑鬼？係邊個令到大家失去相互嘅信任？<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n尋日手足的確唔理想，唔完美，可以改善，但係我地唔割，不分化、不督灰、不割蓆！！</span></span>"},{"pid":"9b6558c30a4b618ca9778ebc0b6c52be7ff74289","tid":1470312,"uid":182291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:53:13.000Z","msg":"10 Push"},{"pid":"a2da53ec3aeb572134eff1817139ed0cf1974f79","tid":1470312,"uid":182291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:54:30.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"0b573113e1cdbd24402455c0a73a2e71d905f45f","tid":1470312,"uid":182291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:55:22.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"bf8262bacf574924206620c5fdd16da782383cb8","tid":1470312,"uid":182291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:57:03.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"98fda05318d22b0a7ad7192f00c650109ae0e19c","tid":1470312,"uid":182291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:00:38.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"a7e4ca83ccdc394e68e050d06bc5851de9782b70","tid":1470312,"uid":182291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:04:18.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"0f19e78d74dbc6167f3509399b03d5a9d3f82707","tid":1470312,"uid":182291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:10:43.000Z","msg":"4"}